        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/30383562/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/30383562/" class="">第65页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/dykb/" class=" " title="柏艾伦">柏艾伦</a>
                (All boundaries are conventions)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="30383562">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">进步指的应是为尊重人类多元的权力与义务所做的奋斗。进步的观念——诞生于欧洲也曾数度崩溃于欧洲——必须超越表象的“现代化“，亦即客服种种障碍只是为了要发展资本主义。”文明“绝不能仅被理解为市场与科技的”现代化“。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-02-02 22:07</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>进步指的应是为尊重人类多元的权力与义务所做的奋斗。进步的观念——诞生于欧洲也曾数度崩溃于欧洲——必须超越表象的“现代化“，亦即客服种种障碍只是为了要发展资本主义。”文明“绝不能仅被理解为市场与科技的”现代化“。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/30383562/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2014-02-02 22:07
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
  </ul>
  

    </div>
